arts.ttl: Groningen Boost European Chances with Win over Heracles
arts.sum: Groningen moved into the European Playoff spots with a comfortable 4-1 win over Heracles Almelo. Ninth spot in the Eredivisie will be good enough for a spot in the European playoffs this season and both Groningen and Heracles are in the mix for the spot.
